very highly of him,

21:06.515 --> 21:08.438
that I...

21:09.560 --> 21:11.858
greatly esteem him.

21:13.147 --> 21:16.651
I like him. “Esteem him”?
“Like him”?

21:16.734 --> 21:19.578
Use those insipid words again and I
shall leave the room this instant.

21:19.653 --> 21:24.284
Very well, forgive me. Believe my feelings
to be stronger than I have declared.

21:24.366 --> 21:27.085
But further than that
you must not believe.

21:29.705 --> 21:32.629
Is love a fancy
or a feeling?

21:32.708 --> 21:34.426
Or a Ferrars?

21:34.502 --> 21:36.379
Go to bed.

21:38.088 --> 21:40.637
“L do not attempt
to deny that...

21:40.716 --> 21:42.718
I think very highly of him,

21:42.802 --> 21:44.725
that I...

21:44.804 --> 21:47.523
greatly esteem him,

21:49.391 --> 21:51.485
<i>that</i> I <i>like him.”</i>

